{"tid":1695292,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"10點鐘窗邊叫建議","createTime":"2019-11-05T14:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T17:59:41.000Z","uid":49220,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e4e3ad600fba6ba20f4e092758c9492c11be6883","tid":1695292,"uid":49220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:20:15.000Z","msg":"我明白好多人唔敢當面屌建制區議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終好多人都怕醜, 你亦唔知身邊行過街坊會唔會係死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而我果區見到仲有好多人拎建制區議員傳單,<br />\n反而泛民候選人冇咩人理, 睇到都心噏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果係區選前一星期, 10點鐘一齊窗邊大叫<br />\n踢走＿＿＿(當區建制區議員/候選人名),<br />\n支持＿＿＿(當區泛民區議員/候選人名)<br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫助到區選,<br />\n特別係屋企窗邊叫, 叫同聽的都係街坊, 都係果區選民,<br />\n宣傳效果更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606de3efc4504f0a0a9bebcae4318bd8e47c4c37","tid":1695292,"uid":49220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:25:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cc1bef2578183ac1acfe2808e6b475dc9dfdf87","tid":1695292,"uid":160589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:26:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f37f69a5873dfcccfe0138cee187f271f0503e9","tid":1695292,"uid":160589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:27:04.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"1ff89e21a4c5dfddab3aa1203227c252da99730e","tid":1695292,"uid":276535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:29:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27162ed78213427eb6329083cfea0951a603bace","tid":1695292,"uid":49220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:38:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"118d704b1ff5a0a06263ace2a5cfd5a85fa34bdd","tid":1695292,"uid":49220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:59:41.000Z","msg":"推"}]}